    <p>Give your home a lit­tle makeover this Lu­nar New Year, as you catch up with friends and fam­ily. New fur­ni­ture and fur­nish­ings are yours to pick up at 40 show­rooms with over 70 brands, of­fer­ing dif­fer­ent deals at each corner.</p>
    <p>Each visit is made sweeter for shop­pers, thanks to fan­tas­tic deals and dis­counts avail­able. Those who spend $200 and above qual­ify for free gifts (re­demp­tion at the Cus­tomer Ser­vice Counter at Lobby B), along with a chance to win a Smeg Toaster and Ket­tle break­fast set in red. In ad­di­tion, re­ceive a pre­mium gift of choice with any pur­chase worth $2,000 and above, while stocks last.</p>
    <p>An iPad is also up for grabs. Sim­ply take a pic­ture at any of the five Trick Eye Mu­seum booths in the mall, and send in your best photo to the Face­book page (@the­fur­ni­ture­mallsg) by 31 Jan­uary 2021. The most-liked en­try on the con­test post wins.</p>
    <p>The Fur­ni­ture Mall is lo­cated at 10 Toh Guan Road. Visit www.the­fur­ni­ture­mall.com.sg or call them at 6298-1600 for more in­for­ma­tion.</p>

